Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
93-97 Normanby Road is located within the tightly held industrial precinct of Notting Hill which is only 19km’s from the Melbourne CBD. The property is located directly opposite Monash Universtiy and has immediate access to the Monash Freeway via Blackburn and Forster Roads.

Property Features Include:
+ Total Building Area: 3,744sqm*
+ Corporate first floor offices
+ Functional warehouse with multiple roller door access
+ Two cranes
+ Small but secure rear yard

*denotes approx

Located in the heart of the thriving Monash Industrial precinct, opportunities of this size are rarely offered to the market. The property has immediate access to the Monash Freeway via Blackburn and Forster Roads which can connect you directly to the Melbourne CBD or outbound towards Eastlink.

Property features:
+ Total building area: 11,258sqm*
+ Refurbished office/showroom accommodation situated on one level
+ Flexible warehouse areas: 3,400sqm*, 6,510sqm* or 11,200sqm*
+ Fully sprinklered high clearance warehouse 8.2m - 11.1m
+ 8 roller shutter doors
+ Suitable for corporate head office, showroom and distribution centre
+ 128 car spaces with some undercover and basement parking
+ Available now

*denotes approx

This location has convenient connectivity to key transport links providing staff, clients and/or customers with efficient access. The site is located on Blackburn Road between Wellington and Ferntree Gully Roads only moments from the Monash Freeway and Princes Highway.

- Office/warehouse facility with a NLA of 382sqm*
- Corporate style office over two levels and amenities on ground level 252sqm*
- High clearance (6m) warehouse of 65sqm*
- Tech/lab area 72sqm*
- 7 car parks on title
- Amenities on ground floor include two toilets and a kitchen
- Container height roller door
- 3 phase power

Comprising 287sqm* of high quality corporate style office and a 134sqm* high clearance warehouse, this is 421sqm* of prime tenancy for a business that’s serious about their corporate image.

Situated in Melbourne’s geographical centre and only a short 19km* drive from the CBD, Uni Central boasts outstanding access to major arterials - including Monash Freeway, Blackburn Road & Princes Highway. Neighbouring Monash University, CSIRO and the Synchrotron.

16 conveniently located car parks are included on site.
